These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, rock, d&b
1. the fan of reggae is between the fan of rock and the fan of d&b##2
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | d&b | reggae | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, soy-milk, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite | water | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, snake, fish
1. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the fish##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | horse | fish | snake | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, tomato, lemon, blueberry
1. the person eating lemon is between the person eating tomato and the person eating kiwi##2
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | blueberry | tomato | lemon | kiwi |

